graph TD
    A[Email Trigger] --> B[Select Template]
    B --> C[Render Template]
    C --> D[Prepare Email Data]
    D --> E[Send via Email Service]
    E --> F{Success?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Log Success]
    F -->|No| H[Retry Logic]
    H --> I{Max Retries?}
    I -->|No| E
    I -->|Yes| J[Log Failure]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style G fill:#d4edda
    style J fill:#f8d7da
